tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE SQL_database_logs (
  log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  user_id INT,
  action TEXT,
  table_name TEXT,
  query TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE data_privacy_compliance ( 
	id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
	user_id INT, 
	access_time TIMESTAMP, 
	access_type VARCHAR(50), 
	table_name VARCHAR(50) 
);

CREATE TABLE access_patterns ( 
	id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
	user_id INT, 
	login_time TIMESTAMP, 
	query_text TEXT, 
	query_time DECIMAL(10,2) 
);

CREATE TABLE risk_assessment_log (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    action VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE user_access_log (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    table_name VARCHAR(50),
    accessed_columns VARCHAR(100),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE compliance_rating (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    rating INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE risk_assessments (
  assessment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  risk_id INT,
  user_id INT,
  assessment_date DATE,
  assessment_result TEXT
);
